thread.title: Andrey T
thread.title_full: Store DJ reviewed by Andrey T

author: Andrey T
title: Andrey T
text:
My N1 store for anything EDM-related.
Very good, provide discounts and treat you properly even if you are an absolute newbie.
Very rich selection of gear on display that can be tried in-store.
The only thing that keeps me from giving 5 stars is the fact that sometimes they are really busy and sometimes inventory moves too fast to track what's in stock.
Give them a call before ordering/coming to make sure what you want is still in stock, and everything will be fine.
